textAnnotations.description:
KEYSTART
Home Loans
Keystart Loans Ltd gives notice that for existing
clients prior to and including 16th October 2009
the variable interest rate will be reduced to 4.38%pa.
Effective 14th July 2017.
For clients loans from 16th October 2009 the
variable interest rate will be reduced to 5.16%pa.
Effective 14h July 2017
ABN: 27009 427 034
Australian Credit License: 381437
